Description: embeds trustmanager 3.1.4 in the lib directory.
 EMI Trustmanager 3.1.4 does not have a Debian package (yet).
 The assembly embeds trustmanager 3.1.4 from the SWITCH maven repo into
 the lib directory.
Author: Valery Tschopp <valery.tschopp@switch.ch>
